00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:30,520
But sometimes people say that final offer in a negotiation when you're bargaining with the seller.

65
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:36,390
Bargaining with the seller would you be willing to consider this if you want to get somebody to do something

66
00:03:36,540 --> 00:03:38,320
