Could you meet me in the middle on this please.

77
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:09,300
All right.

78
00:04:09,570 --> 00:04:11,070
All right I guess so.

79
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,250
You've got a deal.

80
00:04:12,350 --> 00:04:13,050
OK.

